on my say‐so ♪

30:28.660 --> 30:31.463
♪ Ay, get money,
yeah, we get dough ♪

30:31.496 --> 30:32.898
[water bubbling]

30:32.931 --> 30:34.466
♪ Numbers, all I wanna see,
[...] ♪

30:34.499 --> 30:36.835
♪ I be on the ball
like a free kick ♪

30:36.868 --> 30:38.704
♪ Long haul,
I don't do quick ♪

30:38.737 --> 30:40.806
♪ Tell her get loose,
we don't do stiff ♪

30:40.839 --> 30:43.575
‐ Yeah!
‐ Drink two!

30:43.608 --> 30:45.277
[laughter]

30:47.546 --> 30:48.714
‐ I win.

30:48.747 --> 30:50.349
[cup rattles]

30:50.382 --> 30:51.316
‐ Oh!

30:51.350 --> 30:52.684
[knock on door]

30:52.718 --> 30:54.586
[laughter]

30:54.619 --> 30:56.555
‐ I won, sorry.

30:58.657 --> 31:00.826
‐ We heard the party
from across the hall.

31:00.859 --> 31:03.729
Musta missed
my engraved invite.

31:03.762 --> 31:04.930
You wouldn't kick me out,
would you,

31:04.963 --> 31:07.833
a pretty thing
like you, huh?

31:07.866 --> 31:09.568
‐ Fuck off, dude.

31:09.601 --> 31:12.671
[indistinct chatter]

31:17.743 --> 31:20.712
All of you go,
go, fuck off.

31:20.746 --> 31:22.180
Get in.

31:26.218 --> 31:28.353
‐ Shit,
the JV showed.

31:28.387 --> 31:30.188
‐ A condition, though.

31:32.758 --> 31:35.427
Turn 'em over.
House rules.

31:38.597 --> 31:40.399
Thank you.

31:40.432 --> 31:42.601
[chuckles]

31:42.634 --> 31:44.403
‐ Are those girls even 16?

31:45.771 --> 31:47.806
This is gonna look really bad
if the sarge finds out.

31:47.839 --> 31:50.308
‐ He won't,
not this time.

31:50.342 --> 31:52.444
[chuckles]

31:54.679 --> 31:56.248
Lean back.
Have some fun.

31:56.281 --> 31:58.283
It's called a night off.

31:58.316 --> 32:01.319
[percussive hip‐hop music
playing]

32:01.353 --> 32:08.393
♪ ♪

32:09.694 --> 32:12.898
‐ Chug, chug, DJ!

32:12.931 --> 32:15.967
‐ ♪ I'm tryna be a gentleman ♪

32:16.001 --> 32:18.403
♪ You be acting
like you always do ♪

32:18.437 --> 32:20.472
♪ Hey, girl, I'ma give you
what you want ♪

32:20.505 --> 32:22.674
♪ I'ma love you
good, good ♪

32:22.707 --> 32:24.376
♪ I love you ♪

32:24.409 --> 32:26.511
‐ Yes, this is the room.

32:26.545 --> 32:28.413
[water bubbling]

32:29.381 --> 32:32.417
[dog barks distantly]

32:34.820 --> 32:36.755
[cell phone buzzes]

32:52.904 --> 32:54.639
[phone keyboard clicking]

32:54.673 --> 32:55.807
[phone swoops]

32:57.576 --> 32:59.444
‐ [sighs]

33:00.879 --> 33:02.514
‐ Hey, thanks, man.

33:02.547 --> 33:04.983
I mean, the gun range,
coming to the game,

33:05.016 --> 33:07.018
it‐‐it means a lot.

33:07.052 --> 33:09.821
‐ Hell, it's not like I had
anything better to do.

33:09.855 --> 33:11.623
I know we've been giving you
the hard sell,

33:11.656 --> 33:15.060
but this life
isn't for everybody.

33:15.093 --> 33:16.328
You know,
there are sacrifices,

33:16.361 --> 33:19.431
and it might seem like
an easy decision at 17.

33:19.464 --> 33:22.400
I mean, I know it did
for me, but...

33:22.434 --> 33:26.338
The longer you go, those
people that you leave behind,

33:26.371 --> 33:29.374
well, that's where
they leave you behind.

33:31.877 --> 33:34.779
‐ You mean like
a wife or something?

33:35.947 --> 33:38.416
‐ Or something, yeah.

33:38.450 --> 33:40.685
‐ Shit, was that
how it went for you?

33:42.053 --> 33:44.322
‐ No.

33:44.356 --> 33:46.358
No, I had a wife.

33:46.391 --> 33:49.461
But, uh, I don't have
her anymore, so...

33:52.063 --> 33:52.797
[chuckles]

33:52.831 --> 33:55.066
Sorry, it's a‐‐
it's a long story

33:55.100 --> 33:57.402
best told over something
stronger than this.

33:57.435 --> 33:58.570
‐ Sorry, I mean,
it's‐‐

33:58.603 --> 34:00.438
it's none
of my business anyway.

34:00.472 --> 34:01.907
‐ Ah, don't sweat it.

34:01.940 --> 34:03.909
It happens
to a lot of guys.

34:03.942 --> 34:07.646
Somehow you just
wind up alone.

34:13.151 --> 34:13.852
[bass‐heavy hip‐hop music
playing]

34:15.954 --> 34:17.956
♪ ♪

34:17.989 --> 34:20.559
‐ Hey, where did Beth go?

34:20.592 --> 34:23.995
‐ You're always Beth's girl.

34:24.029 --> 34:26.064
That's why we could
never be tight before.

34:26.097 --> 34:28.600
She never wanted
to share you.

34:28.633 --> 34:30.535
I was always
so afraid of her.

34:30.569 --> 34:33.672
‐ Everyone's
afraid of Beth.

34:33.705 --> 34:35.140
‐ And you.

34:37.309 --> 34:38.610
‐ Me?

34:41.112 --> 34:44.082
[ethereal music]

34:44.115 --> 34:51.122
♪ ♪

35:52.283 --> 35:54.152
‐ Hey, give it to me!
‐ No!

35:54.185 --> 35:57.422
‐ Hey, up yours, whore.

35:57.455 --> 35:58.690
‐ You're a limp dick
piece of shit.

35:58.723 --> 36:01.092
‐ Just give it.
[grunts]

36:01.126 --> 36:02.694
‐ I'm calling the police!
It's ringing!

36:02.727 --> 36:04.729
I want the police here
right away.

36:04.763 --> 36:07.165
‐ Hey, there's
something happening.

36:07.198 --> 36:08.566
‐ In the parking lot.

36:08.600 --> 36:10.335
‐ Oh, he's
calling the cops.

36:10.368 --> 36:11.569
We gotta get you guys
out of here.

36:11.603 --> 36:12.570
Come on.
‐ Shit.

36:12.604 --> 36:14.673
‐ All right, all of you,
this is not a drill.

36:14.706 --> 36:15.774
The party's over.
Come on.

36:15.807 --> 36:16.675
‐ We gotta go.
We gotta go.

36:16.708 --> 36:19.277
‐ Phones!
‐ The other room.

36:19.310 --> 36:20.679
‐ Okay, come on, let's go.

36:20.712 --> 36:23.014
‐ Beth, where's Beth?

36:23.048 --> 36:24.716
‐ [whispers]
Beth?

36:24.749 --> 36:25.717
[door rattles]

36:25.750 --> 36:27.552
Can you open the door?

36:32.557 --> 36:34.092
‐ Bro, you gotta wake up.

36:34.125 --> 36:35.060
Dude, wake up.

36:36.127 --> 36:37.762
The cops'll be here any minute.

36:37.796 --> 36:39.464
Kurtz, you gotta wake up, bro.

36:39.497 --> 36:41.433
‐ Shit, this is Beth's.

36:41.466 --> 36:43.101
She's gotta still be here.
‐ Uh‐uh.

36:43.134 --> 36:44.469
We don't have
time for this.

36:44.502 --> 36:45.804
You know
how bad this looks?

36:45.837 --> 36:46.871
‐ I'm not leaving her.

36:46.905 --> 36:48.606
You need to get
out of here, okay?

36:48.640 --> 36:49.808
Fucking go now.

36:49.841 --> 36:52.377
You...

36:52.410 --> 36:54.112
help me.

36:54.145 --> 36:56.247
[ominous music]

36:56.281 --> 36:58.349
Hey, have you seen my fr‐‐

36:58.383 --> 36:59.651
Ugh, forget it.

36:59.684 --> 37:01.319
Beth?
[knocks on door]

37:01.352 --> 37:02.487
[pounds on door]

37:02.520 --> 37:04.289
Beth?

37:04.322 --> 37:06.624
♪ ♪

37:06.658 --> 37:08.560
‐ What are you talking about?
‐ Just give it back.

37:08.593 --> 37:09.661
‐ Beth?

37:09.694 --> 37:10.895
[tires squealing]

37:10.929 --> 37:12.163
Beth?

37:12.197 --> 37:13.264
‐ Look, I'm sure
it's okay.

37:13.298 --> 37:15.400
Girls like that know
how to handle themselves.

37:15.433 --> 37:17.202
‐ You don't know what the fuck
you're talking about.

37:17.235 --> 37:19.671
[engines revving]

37:19.704 --> 37:21.439
She's down there.

37:21.473 --> 37:22.340
Hey, come on.

37:22.373 --> 37:24.642
[tires squealing]

37:25.844 --> 37:27.645
Hey.
‐ What?

37:27.679 --> 37:29.147
‐ Are you okay?

37:29.180 --> 37:30.482
Did somebody
do something to you?

37:30.515 --> 37:32.117
‐ [groans]

37:32.150 --> 37:33.585
‐ Did someone slip you a pill?

37:33.618 --> 37:35.353
‐ [groans]
‐ Where were you?

37:35.386 --> 37:37.655
Hey.
‐ [mumbles indistinctly]

37:37.689 --> 37:39.023
‐ What are you saying?

37:39.057 --> 37:40.425
Please?
‐ [weakly] Your bracelet.

37:40.458 --> 37:42.594
‐ What?
‐ Your bracelet.

37:42.627 --> 37:44.429
[sirens wailing]

37:44.462 --> 37:46.297
‐ Fuck it.
Let's just wait for the cops.

37:46.331 --> 37:47.098
They'll know what to do
when they get here.

37:47.132 --> 37:48.566
‐ No, we're not
doing that.

37:48.600 --> 37:49.334
My mom's a cop.

37:49.367 --> 37:51.302
‐ Well, what if
she took something?

37:51.336 --> 37:52.437
‐ Can you just go?
You're not helping.

37:52.470 --> 37:54.272
‐ Okay, so you're sure
you can handle this?

37:54.305 --> 37:57.142
‐ Yes! Seriously.
Go!

37:57.175 --> 37:58.810
[sirens wailing]

37:58.843 --> 38:00.745
Okay, we got it.

38:10.255 --> 38:13.458
‐ My husband, you were anxious
to talk to him, weren't you?

38:13.491 --> 38:15.026
‐ Yeah, I was, but

38:15.059 --> 38:16.628
I'm sort of getting over the
idea, if you know what I mean.

38:16.661 --> 38:19.798
‐ There's a speed limit
in this state, Mr. Neff,

38:19.831 --> 38:21.466
45 miles an hour.

38:21.499 --> 38:23.268
‐ How fast was I going,
Officer?

38:23.301 --> 38:24.502
‐ I'd say around 90.

38:24.536 --> 38:26.171
‐ Suppose you get down
off your motorcycle

38:26.204 --> 38:27.305
and give me a ticket.
[cell phone buzzes]

38:27.338 --> 38:29.541
‐ Suppose I let you off
with a warning this time.

38:29.574 --> 38:31.709
[TV turns off]

38:31.743 --> 38:34.179
[cell phone buzzes]

38:35.814 --> 38:38.483
[cell phone buzzes]
‐ [inhales]

38:49.561 --> 38:51.863
Honey, no, no.

38:51.896 --> 38:53.665
You cannot bring her here,
not tonight.

38:53.698 --> 38:54.899
It is not a good night.

38:55.867 --> 38:58.169
[ominous music]

38:58.203 --> 38:59.737
Take her to your house.

38:59.771 --> 39:01.339
Your mom will know what to do.

39:02.607 --> 39:05.677
Look, okay, yeah, uh‐huh,

39:05.710 --> 39:07.345
I know that you think
that you're in trouble,

39:07.378 --> 39:08.613
but you're not, okay?

39:08.646 --> 39:11.382
Are you her friend?

39:11.416 --> 39:13.284
Uh‐huh, uh‐‐

39:13.318 --> 39:15.687
So be her friend.

39:15.720 --> 39:17.355
Fix it.

39:17.388 --> 39:19.224
[door clicks]

39:20.558 --> 39:23.294
Hanlon, the bitch
is your problem.

39:23.328 --> 39:24.629
[phone beeps]

39:24.662 --> 39:27.465
[pounds on door]

39:27.498 --> 39:29.467
‐ Colette, who's there?

39:29.500 --> 39:31.236
‐ I got it.

39:35.406 --> 39:37.642
I thought you were
smarter than this.

39:37.675 --> 39:39.611
Get in.

39:46.584 --> 39:47.785
[door slams]

40:11.376 --> 40:13.278
[mirror squeaks]

40:20.451 --> 40:22.487
[mirror squeaks]

40:24.055 --> 40:25.857
You clearly came here because
you need something from me.

40:25.890 --> 40:26.958
What do you want me to do?

40:26.991 --> 40:28.126
‐ I don't know,
I just thought

40:28.159 --> 40:31.329
that you could help,
maybe help her.

40:31.362 --> 40:32.430
‐ Help her?

40:32.463 --> 40:33.665
What, help her
get less drunk?

40:33.698 --> 40:35.934
I think you know how to get
less drunk, don't you?

40:35.967 --> 40:37.068
You wait.

40:37.101 --> 40:38.536
You go home
and you sleep.

40:38.569 --> 40:40.104
You do not
come to my house.

40:40.138 --> 40:41.439
‐ I found her passed out
in my car.

40:41.472 --> 40:42.373
I thought maybe‐‐

40:42.407 --> 40:45.009
‐ I told you not to come here,
not tonight.

40:46.044 --> 40:48.680
What are we supposed
to tell him about this?

40:48.713 --> 40:49.714
How are we supposed
to explain this?

40:49.747 --> 40:52.750
‐ I'm sorry, Coach,
but you don't understand.

40:52.784 --> 40:54.652
The cops were coming,

40:54.686 --> 40:56.354
and Sarge Will's guys
were there.

40:56.387 --> 40:59.457
‐ Shut...up.

40:59.490 --> 41:00.725
‐ [whispers]
Sorry.

41:00.758 --> 41:02.126
I'm sorry.

41:02.160 --> 41:04.529
‐ I am not your mother,
Hanlon.

41:05.997 --> 41:08.933
I expected more from you,
so much more.

41:10.535 --> 41:11.803
[ominous music]

41:11.836 --> 41:14.806
‐ Dutiful daughter,

41:14.839 --> 41:19.077
happy wife, devoted mother,

41:19.110 --> 41:22.380
all‐American girl,

41:22.413 --> 41:25.483
these are the masks we wear,

41:25.516 --> 41:26.684
all of us...

41:26.718 --> 41:30.388
♪ ♪

41:30.421 --> 41:32.423
All the time,

41:32.457 --> 41:34.058
everything in place,

41:34.092 --> 41:36.527
the smile always there,

41:36.561 --> 41:40.264
never slipping, not once.

41:40.298 --> 41:43.668
"You must be strong,"
Coach said.

41:43.701 --> 41:45.670
"You must be vigilant,

41:45.703 --> 41:48.773
"and here's
the most important thing:

41:48.806 --> 41:50.742
"never show yourself.

41:50.775 --> 41:52.944
No one wants to see
the real you."

41:52.977 --> 41:54.512
[ominous music swells]

41:54.545 --> 41:55.646
[camera shutter clicks]
